    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1e0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-19a.91" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T22:55:02.107+09:00">難道又能够划一不变吗？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-35a.78" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T23:00:42.897+09:00">心里不明白这些，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-35a.79" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T23:00:53.042+09:00">就会混乱各种事物的节度。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-35a.80" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T23:01:34.538+09:00">现在恐怕体气专用在一处，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-35a.81" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T23:01:43.01+09:00">就生病了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-255a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T23:34:38.41+09:00">现在的做法可以说苟且轻薄得过分了，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-255a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T23:34:58.307+09:00">而把人同牲畜一样使用，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-256a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T23:35:20.689+09:00">上天将赐福给谁呀！”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_010-637a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-12T23:46:07.627+09:00">专门倒行逆施。说先王即位有什么常规</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:27:58.491+09:00">那个人只具备其一，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:28:21.182+09:00">恐怕不得善终吧！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:29:23.191+09:00">上天属于刚强的德行，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:29:30.602+09:00">尚且还不触犯寒暑四时的次序，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:29:35.552+09:00">何况在人事上呢？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:29:43.402+09:00">而且华而不实，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:30:10.751+09:00">就会聚集怨恨,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:30:21.659+09:00">触犯别人而聚集怨恨，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:30:30.096+09:00">不能够安定自身。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-98a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:30:44.21+09:00">我害怕不能得到利益反而遭到祸害，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-99a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:30:55.829+09:00">因此才离开他。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1e0001_tls_006-100a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-27T02:31:07.478+09:00">晋国的赵衰、栾枝、先且居、胥臣都死了。</seg>
                </p>
